Setup¶

TagUI is in v5.11 - it unzips and runs directly on Windows, macOS, Linux (link to release notes).

  1. Install OpenJDK v8 (64-bit) or later

  2. Avoid spaces in the folder path of TagUI

macOS¶

unzip and run

Linux¶

unzip and run

Windows¶

unzip and run

Node.js (macOS/Linux)¶

npm install tagui

Cutting Edge Version¶

To use the latest features and fixes, download the cutting edge version and overwrite the packaged installation.
